{"tid":1278094,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 推出 Fast Share，一個兼容 iPhone 的 Android 版「AirDrop」！","createTime":"2019-07-02T11:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T00:05:46.000Z","uid":159448,"like":13,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"668a4aaa112af7bf822729251fec0d093c6ef0b8","tid":1278094,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"據 9to5Google 報導，目前 Google 正在開發全新、簡單的跨裝置文件共享工具 Fas t Share ，並給出了更多新的消息以及操作示範。 Fast Share強調無需聯網就能與附近設備共享文件檔案，有點類似於 Apple 的 AirDrop。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，Android 版的 Fast Share 可以用於分享手機端的圖像和其他文件，以及 URL鏈接和文本片段，在沒有網絡連接的情況下可以向就近的設 備進行傳輸，有如 Google 現時已經在 Android 平台上推出的「Files by Google」的強化版。<br />\n<br />\n該功能圖示會出現在系統分享列表中，目前使用 Google 藍色鑽石外形設計的 Nearby 圖標。或者，可以通過前往系統設置 &gt;Google&gt;Fast Share 來啟動共享過程。雖然，Google 一早推出的 Android Beam 就已經能實現類似的功能。不過，由於需要配對的兩款手機都支援 NFC 功能，而且操作上不太方便，所以 Google 已經決定在 Android Q 上淘汰該功能。而在Fast Share 中，兩款手機則是通過藍牙實現配對，然後通過 WiFi 來傳輸文件，跟「Files by Google」的做法類似。<br />\n<br />\n目前， 小米和華為等國產手機廠商都已經提供了類似的服務，例如小米的快傳、華為的 Huawei Share 等，但它們一般都局限於同個品牌的手機。而Google 這次推出的 Fast Share 將支援所有 Android 平台、Chromebook，甚至是 iPhone 等設備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/07/02/google-fast-share-for-android/?fbclid=IwAR2r-WKidwj3yzPgnAS6M_IlGkn04pCcasVaZHtrNt2zQownCmEBkVWcGXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F07%2F02%2Fgoogle-fast-share-for-android%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2r-WKidwj3yzPgnAS6M_IlGkn04pCcasVaZHtrNt2zQownCmEBkVWcGXc&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=92577100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/07/02/google-fast-share-for-android/?fbclid=IwAR2r-WKidwj3yzPgnAS6M_IlGkn04pCcasVaZHtrNt2zQownCmEBkVWcGXc</a>"},{"pid":"624b550ccecd60f39229e0f0b7ea48f384486c92","tid":1278094,"uid":21378,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"滿意"},{"pid":"d012899f8d4d97be4c22244f080b29ac5821b093","tid":1278094,"uid":197393,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:16:50.000Z","msg":"放心，要裝app嘅話啲人都係會繼續用Airdrop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f2b2119b17ba9722d72ebe769607447ec72d70","tid":1278094,"uid":89514,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T21:54:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d6f818eda53724fabdc767a4de66c7eb7fc338b","tid":1278094,"uid":53440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d012899f8d4d97be4c22244f080b29ac5821b093","tid":1278094,"uid":197393,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:16:50.000Z","msg":"放心，要裝app嘅話啲人都係會繼續用Airdrop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:54:00.000Z","msg":"真係要內置先得"},{"pid":"464738e389e527b4fe586b448023316c9f0954ea","tid":1278094,"uid":108146,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:55:15.000Z","msg":"等睇瘋狂中毒"},{"pid":"367cc5300fb2d1a5987f8d5a1837fdcce8377c97","tid":1278094,"uid":159913,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:55:53.000Z","msg":"終於可以Android幫手遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07059b5fc32d936846041135d94277dc42b4e315","tid":1278094,"uid":140167,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:26:15.000Z","msg":"係好事.<br />\n快啲出, 發夢嗰陣 An 機巴絲都可以幫手 Share 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c99a0777382e38db0a3e1dd1aa2f878aa87e767","tid":1278094,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:17:57.000Z","msg":"雙修朋友嘅褔音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ef80205681a6e00fa29ff7ef7b57e60d9014c2","tid":1278094,"uid":67692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"367cc5300fb2d1a5987f8d5a1837fdcce8377c97","